data.description:
581 Brittany M, Delray Beach, FL 33446 is a condo home that contains 883 sq ft and was built in 1974. It contains 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This home last sold for $115,000 in February 2022. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $162,200. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $1,700/mo.
data.whatILove: If you've been searching for a move-in-ready home that seamlessly blends style, comfort, and convenience, look no further! This 2-bedroom, 2-bath at kings point home has been completely renovated and has a brand new  water heater, granite counter top, new stainless steel appliances, window treatments,  brain new wall A/C and sensor light  in the laundry room, walking closet with ceiling fan and light in master bedroom, lovely wooden blinds in all widows easy to manage.  Delray Beach offers a vibrant community with a range of amenities and activities. From nearby parks and golf courses to shopping centers and dining options, you'll find everything you need within easy reach. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this home your own! All reasonable writing offers are considered!
